title: Apt #2107 Ideal WFH Floor Plan! Available Now. 50% Off Parking
posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 30', 'OR Text', '30', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our leasing team.', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 867 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'We are now conducting both self-guided and guided tours!', 'Offering luxury high-rise living in a bustling city center, One South Market apartments takes you to new HEIGHTS in the heart of Downtown San Jose, California.', 'When it’s time to hit the town, an array of restaurants and cafés are at your doorstep.', 'Venture a little farther and shop at Santana Row or cheer on the San Jose Sharks at the SAP Center.', 'One South Market is central and convenient with the VTA Light Rail and Caltrain just minutes away.', 'Close to major commute routes on highways 87, 101, and I-280–putting all of Silicon Valley within your reach.', '***Prices are subject to change on a daily basis***', 'Features:', 'Floor to Ceiling Windows, Central Air Conditioning and Heat, In-Unit Washer/Dryer, Hardwood-Style Vinyl Flooring, Kitchen Island, Great View, High Ceilings, Stainless Steel Appliances, Large Closets, Quartz Countertops', 'Community Amenities:', 'Controlled Access, EV Charging Stations, Fitness Center, Elevator, LEED Certified, Outdoor Firepit, Pet Friendly*, Bike Storage, Resident Lounge, Swimming Pool, Club Room, Online Rental Payments, Wi-Fi in Common Areas, BBQ Grill', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets - Maximum of 2 allowed per home.', 'Cats - allowed, Rent $50.00, Deposit $500.00', 'Dogs - allowed, Rent $75.00, Deposit $500.00', '*Breed restrictions apply.', 'Please see a Leasing Consultant for details.', 'Income Requirements:', '2.5x the base rent.', 'Use this link for more info:', '<URL>', '7id9kHfIX']
